Subject: RE: [T2] Fuel Injection Fuel Pump

Ford pick-ups, F-150s and rangers 1985 to 1988 have externally mounted bosch
fuel pumps on the frame.  They are cheap and quite common and I'm using one
on my 79, 2.0 F.I. bus with no problems.  

J. Melendy 
79 bus (notabug)

